_sText:
A fun map originally for Minigames, re-make for Deathmatch.

Disclaimer: I am not the author of mg_pushcircle_fix2

This map consist of 12 musics, all fit nicely into the gameplay. All song credits goes to their rightful newgrounds.com authors.

4 Ramps will toggle every minute, opening and closing, so you get two different experiences with and without the ramp.

Buytime has been setup to 5 minutes as default time per round.

Airaccelerate has been changed to 500 in order to have the maximum fun. On top of this, sv_enablebunnyhopping, sv_enableboost has been set to true.

Bombsite has been added so map resets when the time runs out when there are enough players. However, C4 cannot be planted at the bombsite.

Question/Comments/Bug? Leave them here!
Please Rate and explain, thank you very much!
